            <task isForCompensation="false" startQuantity="1" completionQuantity="1" name="Mark person as eligible to reregister" id="_18_5_1_11940316_1499265732973_193572_22420">
                <documentation textFormat="text/plain">The matching record is not added to the list of eligible voters. Instead, if the voter registration database has a record of this person indicating ineligibility to register to vote by court action, the flag is removed or otherwise indicates eligibility to reregister.</documentation>
