                <documentation textFormat="text/plain">The address update may no longer pertain to a record in the voter registration database. The election jurisdiction must find a matching record in order to proceed.</documentation>
                <incoming>_18_5_1_11940316_1499538218570_269807_26107</incoming>
                <outgoing>_18_5_1_11940316_1499538233417_224659_26128</outgoing>
