            </endEvent>
            <task isForCompensation="false" startQuantity="1" completionQuantity="1" name="Compare addresses" id="_18_5_1_11940316_1499538193295_717500_25914">
                <documentation textFormat="text/plain">Even if the address update record shows a newer address, the current state of the voter’s record needs to be examined. It is possible that the update has already been made by other means. This is because address update reports can become stale if they are not processed immediately.</documentation>
                <incoming>_18_5_1_11940316_1499538193299_469490_25922</incoming>
                <outgoing>_18_5_1_11940316_1499538193300_654421_25924</outgoing>
