                <documentation textFormat="text/plain">Update the voting address to the new address identified by the address update record.</documentation>
                <incoming>_18_5_1_11940316_1499538193301_325779_25930</incoming>
                <outgoing>_18_5_1_11940316_1502834761396_767108_41860</outgoing>
